languages.en: //(0,2.736249)\\Well, that was rather impressive.//(2.736249,6.298137)\\You've managed to eliminate all three targets in one fell swoop.//(6.298137,9.591812)\\Excellent work.

languages.it: //(0,2.530924)\\Beh, davvero notevole.//(2.530924,6.311906)\\Sei riuscito a eliminare tre bersagli in un colpo solo.//(6.311906,8.036201)\\Ottimo lavoro, 47.
